      <textAnnotation id="sid-47485D42-4597-49EA-9EE7-6BDFEEF7F5ED" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Except: 
India, China, Brazil, Argentina, Russia
</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-11403FCB-0025-4BAA-8795-CE7B5766472D" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Send Order Confirmation 
to Customer </text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-8D3449AF-BD4E-49DD-B412-01824E5D1F41" signavio:alignment="left">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioType dataObjectType="IT-System"/>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bgcolor" metaValue="#e1e1e1"/>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
            <signavio:signavioLabel bottom="false" left="false" ref="text_name" right="false" top="true" valign="bottom" x="31.0" y="-9.0"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>MPL
For Pack, Mark, Label 
SPECTRUM 
(for Customer Label)</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-4AB49DDF-C0A1-4DB1-B94A-3B94C86EA9E1" signavio:alignment="left">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioType dataObjectType="IT-System"/>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bgcolor" metaValue="#e1e1e1"/>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
            <signavio:signavioLabel bottom="false" left="false" ref="text_name" right="false" top="true" valign="bottom" x="32.0" y="-9.0"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>CIBR (via ECA)
</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-7CF31A50-94A9-4BEE-9D7E-21B7628D2FA2" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>MPL, SPECTRUM doesn’t connect to S/4 directly
</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-30C6F757-0757-4AED-829E-BBE6711E5045" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Customer 
Confirms the  Quote against the PO
</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-EF1C90CD-5AAE-4662-9BD2-D2A9439C55F2" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Pricing details will be loaded in SAP directly
</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-5A4F7164-BE9C-4BC9-A2A6-8D8418DFA594" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>SPL 
Embargo </text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-E34AEEA2-1B13-4B49-8C94-9F5C9941660B" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>DR: Customer (Accounts Receivable)
CR:  Customer (Account Receivable)
</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-433FFF8C-74E2-4DCA-82E4-9D46F0CFECF7" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Reconciliation of Payments 
to open invoices </text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-DFB2E349-E06D-4692-8BAF-3FF30B57991A" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>EDI 810, PIP 3C3
E-Invoice
PDF</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-89929F38-F722-4B52-B0FC-4DD804884893" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Customer Payment
ACH/WIRE
</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-E9031AF4-06A9-40BE-B180-1FE5B66956E4" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Financial Posting will be replicated real-time from individual S4 box to CFIN system
</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-2BFCE045-C476-4C52-9D58-E2A6787A282D" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>MVT type: 101
Dr. Inventory
Cr. GR/IR
</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-F979B68D-ED19-4E0F-ABA9-DEF38503DAEF" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>(Option) Offsetting 
payment against NRE Credits</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-822107AC-935A-4ADB-A682-61EBF9974098" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Financial Posting will be replicated real-time from individual S4 box to CFIN system
</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <group categoryValueRef="sid-9d85f3aa-2588-4187-9f5b-5bd40348cc71" id="sid-DDA9CB34-20D2-4669-915B-AB949F87DBCF">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
      </group>
      <group id="sid-A0530B89-7CFD-4329-A68B-A0485E8F6752">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#FF6600"/>
         </extensionElements>
      </group>
      <group categoryValueRef="sid-c4a966ac-2658-49b1-8ca0-1ab8f5cb9474" id="sid-AE0E1EF5-F0BF-4929-8398-F7A4066D7F0C">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#339966"/>
            <signavio:signavioLabel bold="" fill="#339966" fontFamily="" fontSize="" italic="" ref="text_name"/>
         </extensionElements>
      </group>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-D44E5E6A-5A9E-4097-BB85-0A68CAA45DA4" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>This flow assumes that we will assign part numbers to masks and track them as inventory until either put into service (expensed) or sold to the customer.
</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-16D20CA5-6CB7-44E0-BB57-26A91F4EBDA3" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>KDD: Mask Part Numbers
We will create part numbers by mask type.  Transactions will be at the type level (e.g., 5 of type 1, 3 of type 2) vs. individual masks.  Pricing and standard costs will be maintained at the type level
</text>
      </textAnnotation>
   </process>
